{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775875976333,"sessionID":"ses_2858b5e14ffecLCunjkJ5rzkBq","part":{"id":"prt_d7a74e6460011t9XfVEU72vMfH","messageID":"msg_d7a74d885001iSeye6L1rP40BA","sessionID":"ses_2858b5e14ffecLCunjkJ5rzkBq","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_e1b53715f28d465e883b42a8","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-033/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-033/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-033: Makefile 构建目标体系\n2: \n3: **Module:** root  \n4: **Language:** Makefile  \n5: **Size:** M  \n6: **Design Stage:** ST-3 completed\n7: \n8: ---\n9: \n10: ## Phase 1: 配置变量 (Configuration Variables)\n11: \n12: - [ ] **T001** 定义全局变量: `DOCKER_REGISTRY`, `DOCKER_TAG`, `GO_VERSION`, `BINARY_VERSION`\n13: - [ ] **T002** 定义二进制配置: `BINARIES`, `GO_LDFLAGS`, `CGO_ENABLED`\n14: - [ ] **T003** 定义构建配置: `GOOS_DEFAULT`, `GOARCH_DEFAULT`, `BUILD_DIR`\n15: - [ ] **T004** 定义测试配置: `TEST_FLAGS`, `COVERAGE_PROFILE`, `COVERAGE_REPORT`\n16: - [ ] **T005** 验证变量定义: 运行 `make -p | grep -E \"^(DOCKER_REGISTRY|BINARY_VERSION|BINARIES)=\"`\n17: \n18: ---\n19: \n20: ## Phase 2: 基础二进制构建 (Binary Build Targets)\n21: \n22: - [ ] **T010** 实现 `build` 目标，构建所有二进制\n23: - [ ] **T011** 实现 `build-router` 目标，构建 `bin/router`\n24: - [ ] **T012** 实现 `build-workload-manager` 目标，构建 `bin/workload-manager`\n25: - [ ] **T013** 实现 `build-agentd` 目标，构建 `bin/agentd`\n26: - [ ] **T014** 实现 `build-picod` 目标，构建 `bin/picod`\n27: - [ ] **T015** 验证: `make build` 成功执行，`bin/` 包含所有 4 个二进制\n28: - [ ] **T016** 验证: `ls -la bin/` 显示正确的可执行文件\n29: \n30: ---\n31: \n32: ## Phase 3: 跨平台编译 (Cross-Compilation Targets)\n33: \n34: - [ ] **T020** 实现 `cross-build` 目标，编译所有平台\n35: - [ ] **T021** 实现 `build-linux-amd64` 目标\n36: - [ ] **T022** 实现 `build-linux-arm64` 目标\n37: - [ ] **T023** 实现 `build-darwin-amd64` 目标\n38: - [ ] **T024** 实现 `build-darwin-arm64` 目标\n39: - [ ] **T025** 验证: `make cross-build` 生成 `bin/linux-amd64/`, `bin/linux-arm64/`, `bin/darwin-amd64/`, `bin/darwin-arm64/`\n40: - [ ] **T026** 验证: 每个平台目录包含所有 4 个二进制\n41: \n42: ---\n43: \n44: ## Phase 4: Docker 构建目标 (Docker Build Targets)\n45: \n46: - [ ] **T030** 实现 `docker-build` 聚合目标\n47: - [ ] **T031** 实现 `docker-build-router` 目标\n48: - [ ] **T032** 实现 `docker-build-workload-manager` 目标\n49: - [ ] **T033** 实现 `docker-build-agentd` 目标\n50: - [ ] **T034** 验证: `make docker-build` 成功构建所有镜像\n51: - [ ] **T035** 验证: `docker images | grep agentcube` 显示 3 个镜像 (router, workload-manager, agentd)\n52: \n53: ---\n54: \n55: ## Phase 5: Docker 推送目标 (Docker Push Targets)\n56: \n57: - [ ] **T040** 实现 `docker-push` 聚合目标\n58: - [ ] **T041** 实现 `docker-push-router` 目标\n59: - [ ] **T042** 实现 `docker-push-workload-manager` 目标\n60: - [ ] **T043** 实现 `docker-push-agentd` 目标\n61: - [ ] **T044** 验证: `make docker-push` 推送镜像到仓库 (需配置 registry)\n62: \n63: ---\n64: \n65: ## Phase 6: 测试目标 (Test Targets)\n66: \n67: - [ ] **T050** 实现 `test` 目标 (默认: test-unit)\n68: - [ ] **T051** 实现 `test-unit` 目标，运行单元测试\n69: - [ ] **T052** 实现 `test-cover` 目标，生成覆盖率报告\n70: - [ ] **T053** 验证: `make test` 执行成功，退出码为 0\n71: - [ ] **T054** 验证: `make test-cover` 生成 `coverage.out` 和 `coverage.html`\n72: \n73: ---\n74: \n75: ## Phase 7: 代码质量目标 (Code Quality Targets)\n76: \n77: - [ ] **T060** 实现 `lint` 目标，运行 golangci-lint\n78: - [ ] **T061** 实现 `lint-fix` 目标，自动修复 lint 问题\n79: - [ ] **T062** 实现 `fmt` 目标，格式化代码 (gofmt, goimports)\n80: - [ ] **T063** 验证: `make lint` 在无错误时退出码为 0\n81: - [ ] **T064** 验证: `make lint-fix` 修复可修复的问题\n82: \n83: ---\n84: \n85: ## Phase 8: 开发环境目标 (Development Targets)\n86: \n87: - [ ] **T070** 实现 `dev` 聚合目标 (默认: dev-docker)\n88: - [ ] **T071** 实现 `dev-docker` 目标，启动 docker-compose 开发环境\n89: - [ ] **T072** 验证: `make dev-docker` 启动服务 (需 docker-compose.dev.yml)\n90: \n91: ---\n92: \n93: ## Phase 9: 清理目标 (Cleanup Targets)\n94: \n95: - [ ] **T080** 实现 `clean` 目标，清理 `bin/` 目录\n96: - [ ] **T081** 实现 `docker-clean` 目标，清理本地镜像\n97: - [ ] **T082** 验证: `make clean` 删除 `bin/` 所有文件\n98: - [ ] **T083** 验证: `make docker-clean` 删除构建的镜像\n99: \n100: ---\n101: \n102: ## Phase 10: 辅助目标 (Utility Targets)\n103: \n104: - [ ] **T090** 实现 `help` 目标，显示分类的目标说明\n105: - [ ] **T091** 实现 `version` 目标，显示 `BINARY_VERSION`\n106: - [ ] **T092** 实现 `deps` 目标，检查 Go、Docker 等依赖\n107: - [ ] **T093** 验证: `make help` 输出包含所有目标类别\n108: - [ ] **T094** 验证: `make version` 输出当前版本\n109: - [ ] **T095** 验证: `make deps` 显示依赖检查结果\n110: \n111: ---\n112: \n113: ## Phase 11: .PHONY 声明\n114: \n115: - [ ] **T100** 声明所有二进制构建目标为 `.PHONY`\n116: - [ ] **T101** 声明所有 Docker 目标为 `.PHONY`\n117: - [ ] **T102** 声明所有测试目标为 `.PHONY`\n118: - [ ] **T103** 声明所有代码质量目标为 `.PHONY`\n119: - [ ] **T104** 声明所有开发、清理、辅助目标为 `.PHONY`\n120: \n121: ---\n122: \n123: ## Phase 12: 错误处理验证\n124: \n125: - [ ] **T110** 验证: 缺少 Go 时显示正确错误信息\n126: - [ ] **T111** 验证: 缺少 Docker 时显示正确错误信息\n127: - [ ] **T112** 验证: 构建失败时传播 Go 错误信息\n128: - [ ] **T113** 验证: 清理不存在的镜像时静默忽略 (使用 `|| true`)\n129: \n130: ---\n131: \n132: ## Phase 13: 验收标准\n133: \n134: - [ ] **T120** `make build` 生成 `bin/{router,workload-manager,agentd,picod}`\n135: - [ ] **T121** `make cross-build` 生成所有 4 个平台目录\n136: - [ ] **T122** `make docker-build` 构建所有镜像\n137: - [ ] **T123** `make test` 执行测试成功\n138: - [ ] **T124** `make test-cover` 生成覆盖率报告\n139: - [ ] **T125** `make lint` 无错误时退出码为 0\n140: - [ ] **T126** `make help` 显示所有目标\n141: - [ ] **T127** `make clean` 清理 `bin/` 目录\n142: - [ ] **T128** 变量可覆盖: `make DOCKER_REGISTRY=custom build`\n143: \n144: ---\n145: \n146: ## Dependencies\n147: \n148: ```\n149: T001-T005 (Config) → T010-T016 (Binary Build)\n150: T010-T016 → T020-T026 (Cross-Compile)\n151: T001-T005 → T030-T035 (Docker Build)\n152: T030-T035 → T040-T044 (Docker Push)\n153: T001-T005 → T050-T054 (Test)\n154: T001-T005 → T060-T064 (Lint)\n155: T001-T005 → T070-T072 (Dev)\n156: T001-T005 → T080-T083 (Cleanup)\n157: T001-T005 → T090-T095 (Utilities)\n158: T001-T095 → T100-T104 (PHONY)\n159: All phases → T110-T113 (Error Handling)\n160: All phases → T120-T128 (Acceptance)\n161: ```\n162: \n163: **Parallel:** T010-T014 (二进制构建) 内部可并行，但通常按顺序执行\n164: \n165: ## Verification Commands\n166: \n167: ```bash\n168: # Binary build\n169: make build\n170: ls -la bin/\n171: \n172: # Cross-compilation\n173: make cross-build\n174: ls -la bin/*-amd64 bin/*-arm64\n175: \n176: # Docker build\n177: make docker-build\n178: docker images | grep agentcube\n179: \n180: # Test\n181: make test\n182: make test-cover\n183: ls coverage.out coverage.html\n184: \n185: # Lint\n186: make lint\n187: make lint-fix\n188: \n189: # Cleanup\n190: make clean\n191: ls bin/  # should be empty\n192: \n193: # Utilities\n194: make help\n195: make version\n196: make deps\n197: ```\n\n(End of file - total 197 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-033: Makefile 构建目标体系\n\n**Module:** root  \n**Language:** Makefile  \n**Size:** M  \n**Design Stage:** ST-3 completed\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: 配置变量 (Configuration Variables)\n\n- [ ] **T001** 定义全局变量: `DOCKER_REGISTRY`, `DOCKER_TAG`, `GO_VERSION`, `BINARY_VERSION`\n- [ ] **T002** 定义二进制配置: `BINARIES`, `GO_LDFLAGS`, `CGO_ENABLED`\n- [ ] **T003** 定义构建配置: `GOOS_DEFAULT`, `GOARCH_DEFAULT`, `BUILD_DIR`\n- [ ] **T004** 定义测试配置: `TEST_FLAGS`, `COVERAGE_PROFILE`, `COVERAGE_REPORT`\n- [ ] **T005** 验证变量定义: 运行 `make -p | grep -E \"^(DOCKER_REGISTRY|BINARY_VERSION|BINARIES)=\"`\n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: 基础二进制构建 (Binary Build Targets)","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-033/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775875976315,"end":1775875976330}}}}
{"type":"step_finish","timestamp":1775875976394,"sessionID":"ses_2858b5e14ffecLCunjkJ5rzkBq","part":{"id":"prt_d7a74ec8c001R1tnmKrw7fV66M","reason":"tool-calls","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","messageID":"msg_d7a74d885001iSeye6L1rP40BA","sessionID":"ses_2858b5e14ffecLCunjkJ5rzkBq","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":22574,"input":258,"output":89,"reasoning":0,"cache":{"write":0,"read":22227}},"cost":0}}
